# Color Grade Trigger
placements.triggers.ExtendedVariantMode/ColorGradeTrigger.tooltips.colorGrade=The color grade to apply. You can add your own one by dropping it in Graphics/ColorGrading in your mod folder.
placements.triggers.ExtendedVariantMode/ColorGradeTrigger.tooltips.revertOnDeath=If checked, the previous value for the Color Grading variant will be restored if the player dies before changing rooms or changing respawn points.
