# Recover Jump Refill
placements.entities.ExtendedVariantMode/RecoverJumpRefill.tooltips.oneUse=Whether the refill should respawn after being used.
placements.entities.ExtendedVariantMode/RecoverJumpRefill.tooltips.texture=The directory, relative to Graphics/Atlases/Gameplay/objects, the refill textures are read from.
placements.entities.ExtendedVariantMode/RecoverJumpRefill.tooltips.respawnTime=The time (in seconds) the crystal will take to respawn (vanilla is 2.5 seconds).
placements.entities.ExtendedVariantMode/RecoverJumpRefill.tooltips.breakEvenWhenFull=If checked, the refill will break even if the player already has the maximum amount of jumps they can get.

